result.name: Night Sky for Roblox
result.description: This is the fixed version of the original, the background works. Browser Warning: Won't appear on Microsoft Edge switch to any other major browser. Lag may be present due to high frames. Moderate Quality Warning: The original was same quality can't do much about it, give me an imgur link to one with better quality. Credits go to >moonyo< for the original style, the earliest poster of this modified gif was this tumblr user from 2013 >Music Gaming Females< but the original came from >Pokemon Black and White 2, this is the trailer<. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles click BoopBop at the top, or click DittoDino below for some mediocre progressbars.
result.notes: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. The original theme was this gray skyish bg for roblox. It's a link. 13 August 2022 - Released 15 August 2022 - Applies solely to Roblox. 17 April 2023 - Revamped style with new base code. 13 August 2023 - 1st anniversary, thanks for 227k installs. 16 August 2023 - Notifications are visible again.
